<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Neigh2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Neigh,</orth> vb. to utter the voice of a horse: <bibl n="shak. ven 262" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 262</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ven 262" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 262</bibl> <bibl n="shak. son 51.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 51, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.113" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 113</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 5.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. V, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.207" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 207</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.1.119" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 1, 119</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 2.2.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. II, 2, 23</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.351" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 351</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.5.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 5, 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.4.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 4, 17</bibl>. With <cit><quote>to:</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 307" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 307</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.112" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 112</bibl>. With <emph>for</emph>: <cit><quote>our steeds for present service n.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 2, 8</bibl></cit> (express their desire for combat by neighing).
